               <p>MR. PHILLIPS conducted the prosecution.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18250407-76-person473">
                  WILLIAM 
                  GEORGE PAUX
               <interp inst="t18250407-76-person473" type="surname" value="GEORGE PAUX"></interp>
