                  </persName>
            . I am officiating clerk of St. Mary-le-bone - I have the register of that parish; here is a register of the marriage of Samuel Avery and 
               <persName id="t18250407-76-victim474" type="victimName">
                  Ann 
                  Kidd
               <interp inst="t18250407-76-victim474" type="surname" value="Kidd"></interp>
